The Match Artist is an absolutely incredible company! I am so  pleased with the photos from my session with Mike S. He was so incredibly encouraging, helpful, supportive and personable. He made the whole experience so much fun and I was continuously amazed at his eye for detail and finding the perfect spot to take photos. In fact, some of my favorite pictures are because Mike would spot a location and suggest we stop to take some more pictures.
I highly recommend The Match Artist and working with Mike as he is incredibly talented, fun to work with and the turnaround time to get my photos after the shoot was super quick!
Thank you so much Match Artist and Mike! I am so grateful to you for these new photos I can now use on my profiles! I absolutely loved the whole entire experience.

originalText.text: Had a great experience working with Mike! Genuinely such a nice guy and a great photographer. He was so easy to work with, and I loved how the photos turned out. I’ve worked with other photographers in the past - but definitely none of Mike’s caliber. I honestly am blown away by his knowledge of his craft, and even beyond that, just how fun the shoot was! I’m definitely going to be calling him again if I ever need photos taken again for any reason. Don’t miss an opportunity to work with him!

originalText.text: At first I was uncomfortable making such a large investment with a company I found on Google. But, I decided to move forward with the process mainly because they checked all of my boxes in what I was looking for. In the Online dating realm, pictures are extremely important and these guys understand what it takes to make a difference. Mike was my photographer and I can't say enough great things about him and the whole experience. We did the photo shoot in Kansas City where I live. Mike is hands down the best photographer I've ever worked with. He made the whole process very easy and stress free. The whole day was a blast and I'm really happy with the quality of pictures I ended up with. Also, I only had to wait 2 days for him to finish the edits and get them over to me. If you're looking to improve your online dating life, then I highly recommend giving this team the opportunity to help.
